Class DriverType

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.vehicle.DriverType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DriverType
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class (a user-defined data type) stores the name (AV or HV), reaction time, and whether the type is AV or not.
